29 May 2008Minister in the Presidency Essop Pahad, accompanied by Mpumalanga Premier Thabang Makwetla and the Chairperson of the National Youth Commission (NYC) Nobulumko Nkondlo, will brief the media on the government s youth development activities for the month of June, as the country prepares to commemorate the 32nd anniversary of the June 16, 1976 uprising.The government will also use this opportunity to celebrate International Children s Day.The details of the briefing are as follows:Date: Sunday, 1 June 2008 Time: 12h00 Venue: Mpumalanga Parks Board (Nelspruit)Enquiries Bongani Mlangeni (GCIS) Cell: 078 402 1016Siyabonga Magadla (NYC) Cell: 083 686 9016Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)